title: Silver Looking for duo
body: Hey all. Im a silver 4 at the moment. Who likes any lanes. Im looking for someone who shares a non toxic attitude and consistancy to play decently to climb :D. Must have some time to play and be able to use voice communications. Cheers add me if interested.

replies.body: I asked you today :,( no reply...anyways since b5 i only play 2 games per day or every 2nd day and friday i play 4 or more since then i am on the series to s5.. Lets hope i get back to g1 and see where my actual rank lays on
